      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个IngressController的状态流转图，核心是从IngressController初始化开始，经过Ready状态，最后能优雅地Shutdown到RedisCache。Ready状态内部要包含EtcdCluster的运作逻辑。",
