    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "EtcdCluster收到任务时从Idle进入Busy，任务完成回到Idle。但Busy也可能因task_failed进入Error状态。Error需要再细分：先Retrying，重试成功回Idle，超过重试限制就到Failed。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Idle",
