    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下层级结构：Ready包含EtcdCluster，EtcdCluster包含Idle/Busy，而Error又嵌套在Ready内部且包含Retrying？还是Error属于EtcdCluster的一部分？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Ready",
        "Error",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Error是Ready的子状态，和EtcdCluster并列都在Ready内部。实际上EtcdCluster只是标记节点，真正的状态机是Idle-Busy-Error-Retrying-Failed这套。Failed最终可以通过reset回到Idle。",
      "elements_involved": [
